<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Lộ Trình Học Tập – Hoan 2026 🔥</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@700;800&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #07090f;
    --surface: #0d1117;
    --card: #111827;
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    --red: #ff4757;
    --gold: #ffd32a;
    --cyan: #00d2d3;
    --green: #2ed573;
    --purple: #a29bfe;
    --blue: #4dabf7;
    --text: #e2e8f0;
    --muted: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    --school-color: #a29bfe;
    --eng-color: #ffd32a;
    --math-color: #4dabf7;
    --sleep-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    --lunch-color: #2ed573;
  }
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── BG PATTERN ── */
  body::before {
    content:'';
    position:fixed;inset:0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 800px 600px at 10% 20%, rgba(255,71,87,0.07) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 600px 400px at 90% 80%, rgba(0,210,211,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 500px 300px at 50% 50%, rgba(255,211,42,0.03) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events:none;
    z-index:0;
  }
  .wrap { position:relative; z-index:1; }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    padding: 64px 24px 48px;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .hero-pill {
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    background: rgba(255,71,87,0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,71,87,0.3);
    border-radius:100px;
    padding:6px 18px;
    font-size:12px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:2px;
    text-transform:uppercase; color: var(--red);
    margin-bottom:28px;
    animation: fadein 0.6s ease both;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
    font-size:clamp(52px,10vw,110px);
    font-weight:800; line-height:0.9;
    letter-spacing:-2px;
    animation: fadein 0.7s 0.1s ease both;
  }
  .hero h1 .name { color:#fff; }
  .hero h1 .goal { color: var(--gold); display:block; }
  .hero h1 .year { color: var(--cyan); font-size:0.6em; display:block; opacity:0.7; }

  .motivation-banner {
    margin: 32px auto 0;
    max-width: 680px;
    padding:20px 28px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,211,42,0.08), rgba(255,71,87,0.06));
    border:1px solid rgba(255,211,42,0.2);
    border-radius:16px;
    animation: fadein 0.8s 0.2s ease both;
  }
  .motivation-text {
    font-size:15px; line-height:1.8; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    font-style:italic;
  }
  .motivation-text strong { color: var(--gold); font-style:normal; }

  .hero-stats {
    display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:0;
    margin: 36px auto 0;
    max-width:560px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:16px;
    overflow:hidden;
    animation: fadein 0.8s 0.3s ease both;
  }
  .stat {
    flex:1; padding:20px 12px;
    border-right:1px solid var(--border);
    text-align:center;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .stat:last-child { border-right:none; }
  .stat:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
  .stat-num {
    font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
    font-size:32px; font-weight:800;
    line-height:1;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size:10px; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase;
    color: var(--muted); margin-top:6px;
  }

  /* ── QUOTE STRIP ── */
  .quote-strip {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,71,87,0.1), rgba(255,211,42,0.08));
    border-top:1px solid rgba(255,71,87,0.15);
    border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,71,87,0.15);
    padding:14px 24px;
    text-align:center;
    font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    overflow:hidden; position:relative;
  }
  .quote-strip span { color: var(--red); }

  /* ── MAIN ── */
  .main { max-width:1120px; margin:0 auto; padding:48px 20px 80px; }

  /* ── SECTION TITLE ── */
  .section-title {
    font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
    font-size:22px; font-weight:800;
    letter-spacing:-0.5px;
    color:#fff;
    margin: 56px 0 24px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px;
  }
  .section-title .icon { font-size:20px; }
  .section-title::after {
    content:'';flex:1;height:1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--border), transparent);
  }

  /* ── ALERT ── */
  .alert {
    background: rgba(255,71,87,0.07);
    border:1px solid rgba(255,71,87,0.25);
    border-left:3px solid var(--red);
    border-radius:12px;
    padding:18px 22px;
    font-size:13.5px; line-height:1.8;
    margin-bottom:8px;
  }
  .alert strong { color: var(--red); }

  /* ── TIME INFO BOX ── */
  .time-info {
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr)); gap:12px;
    margin-bottom:36px;
  }
  .time-slot-card {
    border-radius:12px; padding:16px 18px;
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:12px;
  }
  .time-slot-card.home { background: rgba(46,213,115,0.06); border-color:rgba(46,213,115,0.2); }
  .time-slot-card.school { background: rgba(162,155,254,0.06); border-color:rgba(162,155,254,0.2); }
  .time-slot-icon { font-size:22px; line-height:1; }
  .time-slot-label { font-size:10px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; opacity:0.5; margin-bottom:4px; }
  .time-slot-time { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:700; line-height:1.5; }
  .time-slot-card.home .time-slot-time { color: var(--green); }
  .time-slot-card.school .time-slot-time { color: var(--school-color); }

  /* ── DAY TABS ── */
  .day-tabs {
    display:flex; gap:6px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:24px;
  }
  .day-tab {
    padding:8px 18px; border-radius:8px;
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    background:transparent; color: var(--muted);
    font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;
    font-weight:700; font-size:13px;
    cursor:pointer; transition:all 0.2s; letter-spacing:0.5px;
  }
  .day-tab:hover { border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.25); color:#fff; }
  .day-tab.active {
    background: var(--red); border-color: var(--red); color:#fff;
  }
  .day-tab.weekend.active { background: var(--green); border-color: var(--green); }
  .day-tab.weekend { border-color:rgba(46,213,115,0.3); color:rgba(46,213,115,0.7); }
  .day-tab.weekend:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }

  .schedule-panel { display:none; }
  .schedule-panel.active { display:block; animation: fadein 0.3s ease; }

  /* ── TIMELINE ── */
  .timeline { position:relative; padding-left:28px; }
  .timeline::before {
    content:'';position:absolute;
    left:8px; top:12px; bottom:12px; width:1.5px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--red), rgba(255,71,87,0.1));
  }
  .timeline-item { position:relative; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .timeline-item::before {
    content:'';position:absolute;
    left:-22px; top:18px;
    width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%;
    border:2px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg);
  }
  .timeline-item.eng::before { border-color: var(--eng-color); box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(255,211,42,0.4); }
  .timeline-item.school::before { border-color: var(--school-color); }
  .timeline-item.math::before { border-color: var(--blue); }
  .timeline-item.sleep::before { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
  .timeline-item.lunch::before { border-color: var(--green); }

  /* ── TIME BLOCK ── */
  .time-block {
    border-radius:12px; padding:14px 16px;
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.025);
    display:flex; gap:14px; align-items:flex-start;
    transition: transform 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
    cursor:default;
  }
  .time-block:hover { transform:translateX(3px); }
  .time-block.eng { background:rgba(255,211,42,0.05); border-color:rgba(255,211,42,0.2); }
  .time-block.eng:hover { border-color:rgba(255,211,42,0.4); }
  .time-block.school { background:rgba(162,155,254,0.05); border-color:rgba(162,155,254,0.15); }
  .time-block.math { background:rgba(77,171,247,0.05); border-color:rgba(77,171,247,0.15); }
  .time-block.sleep { background:rgba(255,255,255,0.015); border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
  .time-block.lunch { background:rgba(46,213,115,0.04); border-color:rgba(46,213,115,0.12); }

  .tb-time {
    min-width:80px; font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
    font-size:14px; font-weight:700; line-height:1.4;
    color: var(--muted);
    flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .time-block.eng .tb-time { color: var(--gold); }
  .time-block.school .tb-time { color: var(--school-color); }
  .time-block.math .tb-time { color: var(--blue); }
  .time-block.lunch .tb-time { color: var(--green); }

  .tb-content { flex:1; min-width:0; }
  .tb-title { font-size:13.5px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:4px; color:#fff; }
  .tb-detail { font-size:12px; color: var(--muted); line-height:1.7; }
  .tb-detail strong { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }

  .tb-tags { display:flex; gap:6px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .tag {
    font-size:10px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:1px;
    text-transform:uppercase; padding:2px 9px;
    border-radius:100px;
  }
  .tag-grammar { background:rgba(255,71,87,0.2); color:#ff8080; }
  .tag-vocab { background:rgba(255,211,42,0.15); color: var(--gold); }
  .tag-listen { background:rgba(0,210,211,0.15); color: var(--cyan); }
  .tag-read { background:rgba(46,213,115,0.15); color: var(--green); }
  .tag-exam { background:rgba(162,155,254,0.2); color: var(--purple); }
  .tag-shadow { background:rgba(77,171,247,0.15); color: var(--blue); }

  /* highlight steps */
  .steps { margin-top:6px; }
  .step { display:flex; gap:8px; font-size:12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); padding:3px 0; }
  .step::before { content:'→'; color:rgba(255,71,87,0.6); flex-shrink:0; }

  /* ── PHASE CARDS ── */
  .phases { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(290px,1fr)); gap:16px; }
  .phase-card {
    border-radius:16px; padding:24px;
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--card);
    position:relative; overflow:hidden;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  .phase-card:hover { transform:translateY(-3px); }
  .phase-accent {
    position:absolute; top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;
  }
  .p1 .phase-accent { background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gold),#ffbe76); }
  .p2 .phase-accent { background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--blue),var(--cyan)); }
  .p3 .phase-accent { background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--green),#7bed9f); }
  .phase-num {
    font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size:72px; font-weight:800;
    position:absolute; right:16px; top:8px;
    opacity:0.05; line-height:1;
  }
  .phase-label { font-size:10px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:3px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .p1 .phase-label { color: var(--gold); }
  .p2 .phase-label { color: var(--blue); }
  .p3 .phase-label { color: var(--green); }
  .phase-title { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-size:20px; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .phase-period { font-size:12px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom:16px; }
  .phase-goals { list-style:none; }
  .phase-goals li {
    font-size:12.5px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    padding:6px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
    display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:flex-start; line-height:1.5;
  }
  .phase-goals li:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
  .phase-goals li::before { content:'▸'; opacity:0.4; flex-shrink:0; margin-top:1px; }
  .phase-target {
    margin-top:14px; padding:10px 14px;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border-radius:8px; font-size:12px; font-weight:700;
  }
  .p1 .phase-target { color: var(--gold); }
  .p2 .phase-target { color: var(--blue); }
  .p3 .phase-target { color: var(--green); }

  /* ── ENG GRID ── */
  .eng-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr)); gap:14px; }
  .eng-card {
    background: var(--card); border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:14px; padding:20px;
  }
  .eng-card-hd { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .eng-icon { font-size:22px; }
  .eng-card-title { font-size:14px; font-weight:800; }
  .eng-period { font-size:11px; color: var(--muted); }
  .eng-item {
    font-size:12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    padding:5px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    line-height:1.5;
  }
  .eng-item:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
  .wbadge {
    font-size:10px; font-weight:800;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    padding:2px 8px; border-radius:6px; white-space:nowrap; flex-shrink:0;
  }

  /* ── RESOURCES ── */
  .resources { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(210px,1fr)); gap:14px; }
  .res-card {
    background: var(--card); border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:14px; padding:18px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .res-card:hover { border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.18); }
  .res-type { font-size:10px; font-weight:900; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom:8px; }
  .res-name { font-size:15px; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:4px; }
  .res-desc { font-size:12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); line-height:1.65; }
  .res-tag {
    display:inline-block; margin-top:10px;
    font-size:10px; font-weight:800;
    padding:3px 10px; border-radius:100px;
  }
  .res-free { background:rgba(46,213,115,0.15); color: var(--green); }
  .res-paid { background:rgba(255,211,42,0.1); color: var(--gold); }

  /* ── TIPS ── */
  .tips { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr)); gap:12px; }
  .tip-card {
    background: var(--card); border-radius:12px;
    padding:16px 18px; font-size:13px;
    color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65); line-height:1.75;
    border-left:3px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .tip-card strong { color: var(--gold); display:block; margin-bottom:5px; font-size:14px; }

  /* ── MOTIVATION CARDS ── */
  .motiv-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr)); gap:14px; }
  .motiv-card {
    border-radius:14px; padding:22px;
    text-align:center; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  }
  .motiv-card.m1 { background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,71,87,0.12),rgba(255,71,87,0.04)); border:1px solid rgba(255,71,87,0.2); }
  .motiv-card.m2 { background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,211,42,0.1),rgba(255,211,42,0.03)); border:1px solid rgba(255,211,42,0.15); }
  .motiv-card.m3 { background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(0,210,211,0.08),rgba(0,210,211,0.02)); border:1px solid rgba(0,210,211,0.15); }
  .motiv-card.m4 { background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(46,213,115,0.08),rgba(46,213,115,0.02)); border:1px solid rgba(46,213,115,0.15); }
  .motiv-card.m5 { background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(162,155,254,0.1),rgba(162,155,254,0.02)); border:1px solid rgba(162,155,254,0.15); }
  .motiv-card.m6 { background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(77,171,247,0.08),rgba(77,171,247,0.02)); border:1px solid rgba(77,171,247,0.15); }
  .motiv-emoji { font-size:32px; margin-bottom:12px; display:block; }
  .motiv-quote {
    font-size:13px; font-weight:700; line-height:1.7;
    color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
  }
  .motiv-card.m1 .motiv-quote { color:#ff8080; }
  .motiv-card.m2 .motiv-quote { color: var(--gold); }
  .motiv-card.m3 .motiv-quote { color: var(--cyan); }
  .motiv-card.m4 .motiv-quote { color: var(--green); }
  .motiv-card.m5 .motiv-quote { color: var(--purple); }
  .motiv-card.m6 .motiv-quote { color: var(--blue); }
  .motiv-author { font-size:11px; color: var(--muted); margin-top:8px; }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  .footer {
    text-align:center; padding:48px 20px;
    border-top:1px solid var(--border);
    font-size:13px; color: var(--muted);
  }
  .footer .name-highlight { color: var(--red); font-weight:800; }
  .footer .goal-highlight { color: var(--gold); font-weight:700; }

  @keyframes fadein { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(12px); } to { opacity:1; transform:none; } }

  @media(max-width:600px){
    .hero h1 { letter-spacing:-1px; }
    .tb-time { min-width:64px; font-size:12px; }
    .day-tab { font-size:12px; padding:6px 12px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-pill">🎯 Lộ trình cá nhân hoá</div>
  <h1>
    <span class="name">HOAN</span>
    <span class="goal">BÁCH KHOA</span>
    <span class="year">2026</span>
  </h1>
  <div class="motivation-banner">
    <div class="motivation-text">
      <strong>"Không có ai thất bại vì cố gắng quá nhiều."</strong><br>
      Hoan đang có <strong>mọi thứ cần thiết</strong> để chinh phục Bách Khoa — chỉ cần giữ đúng lịch này mỗi ngày.
      Khối A01 · Toán – Lý – Tiếng Anh · Mục tiêu: <strong>25+ điểm</strong>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">3</div><div class="stat-label">Giai đoạn</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">7+</div><div class="stat-label">Điểm Anh</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">25+</div><div class="stat-label">Tổng điểm</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">2026</div><div class="stat-label">Năm chiến thắng</div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ROTATING QUOTE -->
<div class="quote-strip" id="quoteStrip">
  💬 <span id="quoteText">"Mỗi buổi tối Hoan ngồi học là một bước gần hơn đến Bách Khoa."</span>
</div>

<div class="main">

  <!-- THÔNG BÁO QUAN TRỌNG -->
  <div class="alert">
    ⚠️ <strong>Lưu ý:</strong> Hoan học cả sáng lẫn chiều tại trường. Lịch này được thiết kế <strong>đúng theo giờ Hoan ở nhà</strong>:
    thời gian sáng sớm (00:00–6:45), nghỉ trưa ngắn (11:00–13:45), và buổi tối (17:00–23:59).
    <strong>Không bỏ buổi nào</strong> — kiên trì là vũ khí mạnh nhất của Hoan 💪
  </div>

  <!-- KHUNG GIỜ Ở NHÀ -->
  <div class="section-title"><span class="icon">🏠</span> Khung Giờ Hoan Ở Nhà</div>
  <div class="time-info">
    <div class="time-slot-card home">
      <div class="time-slot-icon">🌙</div>
      <div>
        <div class="time-slot-label">Sáng sớm</div>
        <div class="time-slot-time">00:00 – 06:45<br><span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans';">Học 05:00–06:45 (chỉ 5:00 thức dậy)</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="time-slot-card school">
      <div class="time-slot-icon">🏫</div>
